(2, 1, 1, 'Initial content', '2019-07-09 20:26:41', 162, 4539, '4f6bf8f67e89553853c3b6e8ed0a6111daaa7a2f', '{\"id\":1,\"asset_id\":54,\"title\":\"Getting Started\",\"alias\":\"getting-started\",\"introtext\":\"<p>It\'s easy to get started creating your website. Knowing some of the basics will help.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3>What is a Content Management System?<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>A content management system is software that allows you to create and manage webpages easily by separating the creation of your content from the mechanics required to present it on the web.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>In this site, the content is stored in a <em>database<\\/em>. The look and feel are created by a <em>template<\\/em>. Joomla! brings together the template and your content to create web pages.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3>Logging in<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>To login to your site use the user name and password that were created as part of the installation process. Once logged-in you will be able to create and edit articles and modify some settings.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3>Creating an article<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Once you are logged-in, a new menu will be visible. To create a new article, click on the \\\"Submit Article\\\" link on that menu.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The new article interface gives you a lot of options, but all you need to do is add a title and put something in the content area. To make it easy to find, set the state to published.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div>You can edit an existing article by clicking on the edit icon (this only displays to users who have the right to edit).<\\/div>\\r\\n<h3>Template, site settings, and modules<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>The look and feel of your site is controlled by a template. You can change the site name, background colour, highlights colour and more by editing the template settings. Click the \\\"Template Settings\\\" in the user menu.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The boxes around the main content of the site are called modules. \\u00a0You can modify modules on the current page by moving your cursor to the module and clicking the edit link. Always be sure to save and close any module you edit.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>You can change some site settings such as the site name and description by clicking on the \\\"Site Settings\\\" link.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>More advanced options for templates, site settings, modules, and more are available in the site administrator.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3>Site and Administrator<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Your site actually has two separate sites. The site (also called the front end) is what visitors to your site will see. The administrator (also called the back end) is only used by people managing your site. You can access the administrator by clicking the \\\"Site Administrator\\\" link on the \\\"User Menu\\\" menu (visible once you login) or by adding \\/administrator to the end of your domain name. The same user name and password are used for both sites.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h3>Learn more<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>There is much more to learn about how to use Joomla! to create the website you envision. You can learn much more at the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.joomla.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Joomla! documentation site<\\/a> and on the<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/forum.joomla.org\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"> Joomla! forums<\\/a>.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2013-11-16 00:00:00\",\"created_by\":\"849\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"\",\"modified_by\":null,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2013-11-16 00:00:00\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":1,\"ordering\":null,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":null,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(3, 2, 1, '', '2019-08-20 21:28:24', 162, 4514, '990dcf2c4ecdc09189bb4ba22a4a47527a37b396', '{\"id\":2,\"asset_id\":66,\"title\":\"Institucional\",\"alias\":\"institucional\",\"introtext\":\"<p>A Empresa, surgiu de um grupo de profissionais advindos de grandes empresas auditoria e consultoria, com uma vasta experi\\u00eancia no segmento de atua\\u00e7\\u00e3o, vislumbrando a necessidade premente do mercado de uma empresa \\u00e1gil, formada por profissionais com s\\u00f3lidos conhecimentos e, por isto, com entendimento das necessidades deste mercado, fundaram a CIGMA.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Ao longo da sua funda\\u00e7\\u00e3o, com o permanente superar de desafios, que \\u00e9 uma caracter\\u00edstica inerente as opera\\u00e7\\u00f5es da CIGMA, a estrutura organizacional desenvolveu a caracter\\u00edstica de dinamismo e a versatilidade e os s\\u00f3cios, que re\\u00fanem experi\\u00eancia e valores adquiridos na forma\\u00e7\\u00e3o de suas carreiras atrav\\u00e9s de acompanhamento, consultorias e contabilidade p\\u00fablica, objetivando, cada vez mais fortalecer esta caracter\\u00edstica, se envolvem diretamente na proposi\\u00e7\\u00e3o e execu\\u00e7\\u00e3o dos servi\\u00e7os, movidos pela convic\\u00e7\\u00e3o de que todos os servi\\u00e7os devam ser executados considerando as reais necessidades e expectativas dos clientes, para que elas possam ser plenamente atendidas e at\\u00e9 superadas.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O objetivo da CIGMA \\u00e9 gest\\u00e3o integrada com apoio aos seus clientes na busca constante do \\u00eaxito administrativo p\\u00fablico, atrav\\u00e9s da presta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de servi\\u00e7os que atendam os padr\\u00f5es da contabilidade p\\u00fablica de qualidade, agilidade nas decis\\u00f5es, criatividade nas solu\\u00e7\\u00f5es com custos compat\\u00edveis \\u00e0s necessidades e expectativas dos nossos clientes.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Valores<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Valorizamos a multiplicidade de conhecimentos de nossa equipe e de nossos clientes e procuramos potencializ\\u00e1-los a cada tarefa.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Cumprimos integralmente nossas responsabilidades no que se refere aos trabalhos ofertados e conseq\\u00fcentemente contratados por nossos clientes.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Vis\\u00e3o<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Conquistar o reconhecimento do mercado atrav\\u00e9s da presta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de servi\\u00e7os profissionais diferenciada pela qualidade e integridade de nossa equipe, condu\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\u00e9tica de nosso trabalho, solidez na gest\\u00e3o da nossa empresa e orientados pelos pilares da responsabilidade e pelo compromisso de cada vez mais elevar nossa qualidade de servi\\u00e7o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Miss\\u00e3o<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Desenvolver ambiente favor\\u00e1vel ao apoio ao gestor p\\u00fablico por meio de pr\\u00e1ticas inovadoras aliadas \\u00e0 prud\\u00eancia e \\u00e0 \\u00e9tica, al\\u00e9m de contribuir de forma decisiva para a forma\\u00e7\\u00e3o de equipes mais compromissadas com a\\u00e7\\u00f5es respons\\u00e1veis, atuando na melhoria da administra\\u00e7\\u00e3o p\\u00fablica num todo.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2019-08-20 21:28:24\",\"created_by\":\"162\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-08-20 21:28:24\",\"modified_by\":null,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2019-08-20 21:28:24\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":1,\"ordering\":null,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":null,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(4, 3, 1, '', '2019-08-20 21:31:55', 162, 4202, 'bf3c8f3e386356eda357dc8e52e809c2d1a02490', '{\"id\":3,\"asset_id\":67,\"title\":\"Servi\\u00e7os\",\"alias\":\"servicos\",\"introtext\":\"<h1>Assessoria e Consultoria Cont\\u00e1bil<\\/h1>\\r\\n<h2>Contabilidade P\\u00fablica<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Acompanhamento contabil em obediencia as normas de contabilidade p\\u00fablica e suas legisla\\u00e7\\u00f5es tudo de forma tempestiva. Organiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o e treinamento de equipe, atrav\\u00e9s de consultoria e assessoria especializada. Procedimentos desde a emiss\\u00e3o e classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o contabil,quando necess\\u00e1rio escritua\\u00e7\\u00e3o de balancetes, livros di\\u00e1rio e raz\\u00e3o cont\\u00e1bil at\\u00e9 a elabora\\u00e7\\u00e3o e entrega de presta\\u00e7\\u00f5es de contas ao Tribunal de Contas, SISTN, SIOPS, conv\\u00eanios, etc.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Elaboramos ainda a LDO \\u2013 Lei de Diretrizes Or\\u00e7ament\\u00e1rias, a LOA \\u2013 Lei do Or\\u00e7amento Anual, o PPA \\u2013 Plano Plurianual, em conformidade com a legisla\\u00e7\\u00e3o vigente.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Acompanhamento bimestral e semestralmente dos relat\\u00f3rios correspondentes a Lei de Responsabilidade Fiscal, bimestralmente e Semestralmente.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Acompanhamento do calendario publico e suas obriga\\u00e7\\u00f5es como DIRF, DCTF, DBE e outros.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Consultoria in-loco e a distancia de acordo com a necessidade do cliente.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Recursos Humanos<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Apoio e controle de pessoal;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Folha de pagamento, fechamento mensal, com importa\\u00e7\\u00e3o de dados para SEFIP;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Verifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o da lesgisla\\u00e7\\u00e3o local quanto a concess\\u00e3o de adicionais e vantagens pessoais e sua forma de calculo em conformidade com Plano de Cargos e Sal\\u00e1rios.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Patrim\\u00f4nio<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Implanta\\u00e7\\u00e3o e acompanhamento cadastral de patrim\\u00f4nio.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Elabora\\u00e7\\u00e3o de invent\\u00e1rio geral.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Reavalia\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\/ deprecia\\u00e7\\u00e3o de bens.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Tribut\\u00e1rio<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Implanta\\u00e7\\u00e3o e cobran\\u00e7a de tributos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Implementa\\u00e7\\u00e3o da cobran\\u00e7a da divida ativa.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Gest\\u00e3o Administrativa<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Apoio ao controle interno.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Apoio ao conselho FUNDEB.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Acompanhamento dos gastos constitucionais Pessoal, Sa\\u00fade e Educa\\u00e7\\u00e3o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Verifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o quanto ao andamento dos trabalhos cont\\u00e1beis com emiss\\u00e3o de pareceres, quanto aos dados contabeis apurados como base para concientiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o ao gestor p\\u00fablico.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Relat\\u00f3rios de presta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de contas.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2019-08-20 21:31:55\",\"created_by\":\"162\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-08-20 21:31:55\",\"modified_by\":null,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2019-08-20 21:31:55\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations