(9, 4, 1, '', '2019-08-20 21:50:49', 162, 2719, 'bd3865b8002b3cbda12d988aeb7eba354dc087cf', '{\"id\":4,\"asset_id\":70,\"title\":\"COMUNICADO SICOM N. 05\\/2019\",\"alias\":\"comunicado-sicom-n-05-2019\",\"introtext\":\"<p>O Tribunal de Contas do Estado de Minas Gerais, por meio da Coordenadoria para Desenvolvimento do Sicom, comunica que fica mantida para a presta\\u00e7\\u00e3o das contas anuais do Chefe do Poder Executivo Municipal do exerc\\u00edcio de 2018 a Instru\\u00e7\\u00e3o Normativa n. 04\\/2017.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>Ficam mantidas tamb\\u00e9m para o exerc\\u00edcio de 2019 as seguintes instru\\u00e7\\u00f5es:<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Instru\\u00e7\\u00e3o Normativa n\\u00ba 03, de 29\\/11\\/2017 \\u2013 LRF;<br \\/>Instru\\u00e7\\u00e3o Normativa n\\u00ba 01, de 24\\/08\\/2016 \\u2013 IEGM;<br \\/>Instru\\u00e7\\u00e3o Normativa n\\u00ba 03, de 25\\/11\\/2015, alterada pela Instru\\u00e7\\u00e3o Normativa n\\u00ba 02, de 29\\/11\\/2017 \\u2013 remessas do IP, AM, BLC e DCASP;<br \\/>Instru\\u00e7\\u00e3o Normativa n\\u00ba 04, de 9\\/12\\/2015, alterada pelas Instru\\u00e7\\u00f5es Normativas n\\u00ba 03, de 16\\/11\\/2016, e n\\u00b0 01, de 30\\/08\\/2017 \\u2013 Folha de Pagamento.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2019-08-20 21:50:49\",\"created_by\":\"162\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-08-20 21:50:49\",\"modified_by\":null,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2019-08-20 21:50:49\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\