(16, 5, 1, '', '2019-09-10 20:13:11', 162, 3028, 'd858e92dc3e12f4fa8900f1d68cc8fb75c5b8fec', '{\"id\":5,\"asset_id\":\"71\",\"title\":\"Despesas com pessoal devem ser computadas pelo ente que realizou os gastos\",\"alias\":\"despesas-com-pessoal-devem-ser-computadas-pelo-ente-que-realizou-os-gastos\",\"introtext\":\"<p>O Di\\u00e1rio Oficial de Contas (DOC) publicou, no dia 7 de mar\\u00e7o, a decis\\u00e3o da Corte de Contas determinando que \\u201cas despesas com Pessoal, pagas com recursos decorrentes de transfer\\u00eancias intergovernamentais obrigat\\u00f3rias, devem ser computadas como gastos de pessoal do ente federado que realizou as despesas\\u201d. O procedimento cont\\u00e1bil deve ser registrado a partir do primeiro dia de 2019.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p>A decis\\u00e3o tem car\\u00e1ter geral e foi tomada durante o julgamento do processo de Pedido de Reexame n\\u00ba 924.154, em dezembro do ano passado, referente \\u00e0 presta\\u00e7\\u00e3o de contas do executivo municipal da cidade mineira de Centralina. O processo teve como relator o conselheiro Wanderley \\u00c1vila.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Tanto as publica\\u00e7\\u00f5es realizadas no Di\\u00e1rio Oficial de Contas, quanto as informa\\u00e7\\u00f5es constantes no processo analisado est\\u00e3o dispon\\u00edveis no Portal do TCE na internet, de acordo com a pol\\u00edtica de transpar\\u00eancia da Corte de Contas para os cidad\\u00e3os.<\\/p>\\r\\n<pre>M\\u00e1rcio de \\u00c1vila Rodrigues \\/ CJR<\\/pre>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2019-08-20 21:52:18\",\"created_by\":\"162\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-09-10 20:13:11\",\"modified_by\":\"162\",\"checked_out\":\"162\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2019-09-10 20:12:45\",\"publish_up\":\"2019-08-20 21:52:18\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":3,\"ordering\":\"2\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"0\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(17, 4, 1, '', '2019-09-10 20:17:05', 162, 2742, '206b25a46c1c87cd84c9505086b5bda109996c0d', '{\"id\":4,\"asset_id\":\"70\",\"title\":\"COMUNICADO SICOM N. 05\\/2019\",\"alias\":\"comunicado-sicom-n-05-2019\",\"introtext\":\"<p>O Tribunal de Contas do Estado de Minas Gerais, por meio da Coordenadoria para Desenvolvimento do Sicom, comunica que fica mantida para a presta\\u00e7\\u00e3o das contas anuais do Chefe do Poder Executivo Municipal do exerc\\u00edcio de 2018 a Instru\\u00e7\\u00e3o Normativa n. 04\\/2017.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<h2>Ficam mantidas tamb\\u00e9m para o exerc\\u00edcio de 2019 as seguintes instru\\u00e7\\u00f5es:<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Instru\\u00e7\\u00e3o Normativa n\\u00ba 03, de 29\\/11\\/2017 \\u2013 LRF;<br \\/>Instru\\u00e7\\u00e3o Normativa n\\u00ba 01, de 24\\/08\\/2016 \\u2013 IEGM;<br \\/>Instru\\u00e7\\u00e3o Normativa n\\u00ba 03, de 25\\/11\\/2015, alterada pela Instru\\u00e7\\u00e3o Normativa n\\u00ba 02, de 29\\/11\\/2017 \\u2013 remessas do IP, AM, BLC e DCASP;<br \\/>Instru\\u00e7\\u00e3o Normativa n\\u00ba 04, de 9\\/12\\/2015, alterada pelas Instru\\u00e7\\u00f5es Normativas n\\u00ba 03, de 16\\/11\\/2016, e n\\u00b0 01, de 30\\/08\\/2017 \\u2013 Folha de Pagamento.<\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2019-08-20 21:50:49\",\"created_by\":\"162\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2019-09-10 20:17:05\",\"modified_by\":\"162\",\"checked_out\":\"162\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2019-09-10 20:16:43\",\"publish_up\":\"2019-08-20 21:50:49\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\